frontend: htmx, hyperscript

List common ports with protocol names
port  |  description
------|-----------------------
0     | reserved, system-allocated dynamic port
7     | echo
13    | daytime
14    | previously netstat
20    | FTP data
21    | FTP control
22    | ssh
23    | telnet
25    | SMTP
37    | time
49    | TACAS
53    | DNS
67    | Bootstrap server (used by DHCP)
68    | Bootstrap client (used by DHCP)
69    | TFTP
70    | Gopher
79    | Finger
80    | HTPP
88    | Kerberos
95    | SUPDUP
101   | NIC
102   | TSAO (class 0 protocol)
104   | DICOM
105   | CCS0 Nameserver
107   | RTelnet
113   | Ident (used by IRC) or auth
115   | SFTP
118   | SQL
177   | XDMCP (remote login to X Display manager server)
194   | IRC
220   | IMAP
443   | HTTPS
465   | SMPT over SSL (obsolete) or URL Cisco or SMTPS
502   | Modbus
514   | Remote shell
520   | RIP (Router Information Protocl)
521   | RIPng
525   | Timeserver
530   | RPC
546   | DHCPv6 client
547   | DHCPv6 server
554   | RTSP
593   | HTTP RPC (Microsoft exchange server)
631   | IPP (Internet Printing protocol) or CUPS
636   | LDAPS (Lightweight Directory Access Protocol)
647   | DHCP Failover
666   | doom or airserv-ng (remote control wireless devices)
698   | OLSR (for mobile ad hoc networks)
701   | LMP
802   | MOdbus/Tcp Security
829   | Certificate Management (obtaining PKI)
847   | DHCP Failover
853   | DNS over TLS/QUIC/DTLS
873   | rsync
953   | RNDC (bind remote name control)
989   | FTPS data (FTP over TLS/SSL)
990   | FTPS control (FTP over TLS/SSL)
992   | Telnet over TLS/SSL
993   | IMAPS (IMAP over TLS/SSL)

Get currrently used web ports:
sudo netstat -pltu
Get currrently used ttys
ls /dev/tty*

